 a significant\nsub-population of dynamically formed BBH binaries.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 16 Mar 2020 19:00:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 9 Apr 2020 17:15:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-03"}
