y behavior so that the corresponding force is\nattractive or repulsive depending on the distance.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 16 Mar 2020 22:37:48 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 9 May 2020 13:24:02 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 3 Jul 2020 16:41:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-05"}
