in semiconductor\nqubits may therefore become relevant once the extrinsic sources of relaxation\nhave been reduced.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 17 Mar 2020 09:17:49 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 17 Aug 2020 08:10:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-19"}
